{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_01","textHome":"我是十咎桃子！十六岁，高中一年级。@估计是因为和兄弟一起混养着长大的……@所以不知道我该算做是假小子还是粗神经。@嘛，不过这样也有好处，就是很擅长运动了。@还有，喜欢……偶、偶像……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":101000}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_18","textHome":"依靠大家的帮助，我才能达到这个程度。@所以我会为了大家使用这个力量。@为了大家，一直战斗下去。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_19","textHome":"才到这可不算完！我还能往前冲！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_20","textHome":"好嘞！早点去试试这力量吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_21","textHome":"我已经不是一个人了。有大家的陪伴……@我一定要不断变强才行。@因为，我想要守护大家。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_22","textHome":"为了守护重要的家人和朋友，@除了变强别无他法！@不仅仅是身为魔法少女的成长，@看这强健的腕力、能干的性格，@也挺不错的，对吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_23","textHome":"可别说我是不凑巧的十咎桃子了哦？@就算是遇上不凑巧的战斗，也能出奇制胜！@在无敌的力量面前凑巧与否根本就没关系嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_24","textHome":"终于等到了！那~，今天一起努力吧！@哦！说起来，昨天聊的事儿后面怎么样了？@我还想听！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_25","textHome":"早啊！怎么啦？看上去没什么干劲的样子？@有什么想倾诉的话，我随时都可以听你说哦。@不介意就跟我说说吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_26","textHome":"饿死了啦……「吃饱了才有力气工作」嘛……@哎，差不多该去吃午饭了吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_27","textHome":"哎呀，我来跟随舞蹈挥舞荧光棒吧！@可以的话，你也一起吧！@正好是相对好跟一些的曲子嘛！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_03","textHome":"每次都这样，我总赶上坏时机。有点好笑。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":300}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"tear":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_28","textHome":"呜哇……啊……虽然已经是高中生了，@到这个点还是困了……啊呜。@是不是白天太闹腾了……哈……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0,"tear":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101000,"tear":1}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_29","textHome":"啊嘞？那张DVD是借给玲奈了吗？@哦！不对啊，我有说过要借给玲奈吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.1,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_30","textHome":"准备好了吗？我随时都可以啦。@完成工作可要好好犒劳一下！@结束后一起去喝茶吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_31","textHome":"好啊好啊！肯定应战嘛！@我可是带着最强的队友呢！@一点儿要输的意思也没有！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_32","textHome":"虽然我也有点紧张，但是想到大家都在，@就莫名地有股力量涌现出来了。@团队合作还是很必要嘛。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_33","textHome":"这个玩偶……啊！是偶然捡到的……@还是说……那个……@这么可爱的玩偶……跟我不搭吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":1}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_34","textHome":"对年长的人抱有敬意很重要哦？@因为他们可都是人生的前辈啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_35","textHome":"看偶像表演还是现场好！@因为每次都有新鲜感，@只要感受到那种气氛……就再也停不下来啦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_36","textHome":"呜哇!?什么事啊!?@突然喊我停下，吓到我了……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"id":101000}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_37","textHome":"嘛~虽然玲奈一开始看着很可怕的样子，@但其实心地很善良的！@她倔强的一面，我挺喜欢的哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_04","textHome":"诶!?她也是魔法少女吗!?@还有这种巧合!?"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":300}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_38","textHome":"超强势的玲奈，加上老好人枫！@挺好，挺好！这就是均衡的团队！@看上去不平衡，其实意外地很团结！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_39","textHome":"八千代好厉害啊，她可是专业的模特儿哦。@平时普通地聊着天的人，突然在杂志上看到，@会让人惊讶得叫出声呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_40","textHome":"尽管通过许愿得到了表白的勇气……@喜欢的人却已经有对象了……@这样徒劳无功的事，你怎么看？@所以别人叫我「不凑巧的桃子」。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":101000}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_41","textHome":"好好好好！我知道了啦！@都让你稍微冷静点了啦！@干嘛那么着急呀？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":101000,"motion":1}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_42","textHome":"放轻松，放轻松！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":101000}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":101000,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1010_00_43","textHome":"干脆利落！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_0